---
// Slide 7: Deliverables (3 Output Types)
---

<div class="slide-frame inactive w-full" id="slide-7" data-slide="6">
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-end flex-wrap gap-4">
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <span class="text-sm font-bold text-neonLime uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">
          07 // Tangible Output
        </span>
        <h2 class="font-outfit text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">
          Deliverables (Hasil Nyata)
        </h2>
      </div>
      <span class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-mono">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-neonLime mr-2"></i>Semua output dapat langsung digunakan oleh industri
      </span>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 pt-4">
      <!-- Digital Assets -->
      <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-cardDark to-cardDark/40 border border-white/5 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[220px] hover-lift glow-lime">
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <span class="text-sm font-mono font-bold text-neonLime uppercase tracking-wider">
            01 / Code &amp; Web
          </span>
          <h3 class="font-outfit text-xl font-bold text-white">
            Digital Assets
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            Website landing page responsif, microsite kampanye promosi,
            dan portal digital siap hosting.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-4 border-t border-white/5 flex justify-between items-center text-xs text-slate-500">
          <span>Deployment Ready</span>
          <i class="fa-solid fa-cloud-arrow-up text-neonLime"></i>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Visual Assets -->
      <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-cardDark to-cardDark/40 border border-white/5 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[220px] hover-lift glow-indigo">
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <span class="text-sm font-mono font-bold text-neonIndigo uppercase tracking-wider">
            02 / Design
          </span>
          <h3 class="font-outfit text-xl font-bold text-white">
            Visual Assets
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            Paket lengkap berisi 30–50 aset desain publikasi digital
            &amp; brand campaign material yang orisinal.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-4 border-t border-white/5 flex justify-between items-center text-xs text-slate-500">
          <span>High Resolution</span>
          <i class="fa-solid fa-image text-neonIndigo"></i>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Media Assets -->
      <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-cardDark to-cardDark/40 border border-white/5 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[220px] hover-lift glow-coral">
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <span class="text-sm font-mono font-bold text-neonCoral uppercase tracking-wider">
            03 / Capture
          </span>
          <h3 class="font-outfit text-xl font-bold text-white">
            Media Assets
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            Kompilasi dokumentasi foto &amp; video sinematik berkualitas
            tinggi yang masuk ke bank aset visual Saygon Group.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-4 border-t border-white/5 flex justify-between items-center text-xs text-slate-500">
          <span>Commercial Rights</span>
          <i class="fa-solid fa-film text-neonCoral"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
